<div class="howitworksbox">

<div class="howitworksbanner">So, how does Snowball work?</div>
<p class="howitworksintro">Quite simply, we help you find & amplify brand ambassadors</p>
<div class="ultimatecenter">


<div class="wcydtext">
<h2>
<img src="../images/num1.png"/>
Create your Fan Club
</h2>
<p>
A fan club is designed for your most passionate users. For startups, this is a typically a brand ambassador program. For authors, artists, and musicians this is typically a fan club. 
</p>
</div>



<div class="wcydtext">
<h2>
<img src="../images/num2.png" "align:left" />
Share and Invite Fans to Join
</h2>
<p>
Share your fan club on Facebook, Twitter, your website and other online outlets. Fans who are passionate about your brand will join because they want to support you. 
</p>
</div>


<div class="wcydtext">
<h2>
<img src="../images/num3.png"/>
Empower True Fans</h2>
<p>
The goal of any ambassador program is to get fans to spread your message. On Snowball, you can easily do this by publishing an action for your users to take. This includes Tweets, sharing on Facebook, composing a blog post, attending an event, and others. 
</p>
</div>


<div class="wcydtext">
<h2>
<img src="../images/num4.png"/>
See the Results
</h2>
<p>
Every action your ambassadors take is tracked. You can see who your most active and influential ambassadors are. 
</p>
</div>


<div class="wcydtext">
<h2>
<img src="../images/num5.png"/>
Rewards!
</h2>
<p>
Show your most influential ambassadors that you appreciate their support by giving them cool stuff and members-only events and exclusive offers. 
</p>
</div>
